\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "non-negative-conversion"

\end_inset

Consider the decomposition of a SDD matrix into a positive and a negative
 sum:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A=P-N
\]

\end_inset

with 
\begin_inset Formula $P_{ij}\geq0$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $N_{ij}\geq0$
\end_inset

.
 Then the matrices 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\begin{array}{cc}
P & N\\
N & P
\end{array}\right)\in SDD_{2n}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $P+N\in SDD_{n}$
\end_inset

 and we have the relation:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\log\left|\left(\begin{array}{cc}
P & N\\
N & P
\end{array}\right)\right|=\log\left|P+N\right|+\log\left|P-N\right|
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

